		  "FROM cal.dftapis " +
		  "WHERE fltno='" + fltno + "' " +
		  "AND fdate='" + yy + mm + dd +"' " +
	      "ORDER BY fdate,fltno,depart,empno ";		  
	rs = stmt.executeQuery(sql); 	
